      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SUM_SUSD shall contain a mapping of all the ECUs controls needed for the execution needs of each SW-C. This mapping and specific column entries used for the decision criteria is project specific and may contain the vehicle power mode, battery voltage levels, PN status relevant for SW-Cs"
    },
